## Analysis repos
### Connecticut River
headwaters_ct_river

*  __[Go to repo to see code](https://github.com/anarosner/headwaters_ct_river)__

* Should eventually point to an main page for this analysis repo, too

* Demonstration of model
  * __[Seasonal Means:](http://anarosner.github.io/headwaters_ct_river/seasonal_means.html)__  http://anarosner.github.io/headwaters_ct_river/seasonal_means.html
  * This has yet to be converted to use headwaters package


### Shenendoah National Park region

  * __[Data Prep:](http://anarosner.github.io/headwaters_sdoah/data_prep.html)__  http://anarosner.github.io/headwaters_sdoah/data_prep.html
